			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S236">Mr. Inhofe</sponsor> (for himself,
			 <cosponsor name-id="S299">Mr. Vitter</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S301">Mr.
			 Coburn</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S254">Mr. Enzi</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="S357">Mrs. Fischer</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S342">Mr. Blunt</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S153">Mr.
			 Grassley</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and
